msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "PSP"
msgstr "PSP"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The PlayStation Portable (PSP) was released by Sony in 2004. It was praised for its high-end GPU and bright 4.3 inch screen. The PSP was succeeded by the PSP Go in 2009, and then the PlayStation Vita in 2011."
msgstr "PlayStation Portable (PSP) vydala společnost Sony v roce 2004. Konzole byla oceňována pro výkonné GPU a jasnou 4,3palcovou obrazovku. V roce 2009 na PSP navázalo PSP Go a v roce 2011 PlayStation Vita."

